room_title: Escape room "Maritime Mutiny" by Escape Room Herndon in Washington, D.C.
room_description: The pirate captain Ravensbeard has been cheating you and the crew out of your rightful share of plunder! Now that hornswoggling scoundrel has barricaded himself in his quarters. You and your mates must break in to reclaim what be rightfully yours and send that scurvy dog to Davey Jones' Locker. If you're crafty enough, mayhaps you'll even commandeer the whole galleon.
